ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] Warrior?
ygData.msgSnippet: Yes, there is a warrior yahoo group, but it is always dead. Here is the Warrior Yahoo Group information: Post message: warriors_eq@yahoogroups.com
ygData.messageBody:
Yes, there is a warrior yahoo group, but it is always dead.

Here is the Warrior Yahoo Group information:
Post message: warriors_eq@yahoogroups.com
<mailto:warriors_eq@yahoogroups.com>
Subscribe: warriors_eq-subscribe@yahoogroups.com
<mailto:warriors_eq-subscribe@yahoogroups.com>
Unsubscribe: warriors_eq-unsubscribe@yahoogroups.com
<mailto:warriors_eq-unsubscribe@yahoogroups.com>

Since the group is just about nonexistent, you should stick to the message
boards.

Here are a few of the warrior sites and forums on the net:
http://www.steelwarrior.org/ <http://www.steelwarrior.org/> and the forum
is at http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior
<http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior>
http://forums.interealms.com/warrior/
<http://forums.interealms.com/warrior/>
http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=forum&f=123
<http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=forum&f=123>

Hope this helps!
